# Si4703_Arduino

# This Library is for the Si4703, with lot of Functions like RDS, Auto Search, better volume control etc.

Short introduction, how connect to an Arduino and run on it:

SCLK to A5
SDIO to A4
VCC to 3.3V (Don't connect it to 5V!)
GND to GND (Ground)
Reset to D2 (you can change this, however you like)
GPIO to D3 (you can also change this, hovever you like)

Now open the Demo sketch, upload it and have fun!

